title: Is Lugo Odge of Amprela similar to the Bohann Biotechnology Laboratory?
subtitle: There was some concern about the obvious links between the video game "resident evil" and the outbreak of the new krona virus.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The "Amberela" fantasy of the "resident evil" game shares a slogan with a biotechnology laboratory in Wuhan, Hubei Province, China, where the new krona virus is believed to have developed.
